descriptions: As you can see, I love photography and tends to take photos everywhere I go, with the people I love and the places we had made love in. At times, I can be as crazy as a loon while there are days when I am as sad as night. Here, it would be a collective place filled with memories.  I love to give unselfishly. I love to see people happy because that makes me happy. I have never been selfish and I don’t admire that quality.
